(21, 1, '2017-03-14 16:25:38', '2017-03-14 08:25:38', '做前端的时间久了之后，难免会碰到那种需要配色但是美工又没有时间的问题，所以就逐渐培养了PS相关技能，其中一些常用颜色是经常用到的，如果你也是从事前端工作的，那收集一些常用颜色的rgb值是很有必要的，下面这些图片是从贴吧中盗取的，如果原作者不喜欢被引用，请联系我，肯定会马上删除：\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-22\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3a85e10735fae6cd3f0223040eb30f2443a70f4b-300x267.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"574\" height=\"511\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-23\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/06b6a22bd40735faa50cc6dc9f510fb30e240801-290x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"574\" height=\"594\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-28\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/e26ce0628535e5dd0e842dba77c6a7efcf1b625e-300x278.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"570\" height=\"528\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-27\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/a459a5529822720eac786a9f7acb0a46f31fab54-300x284.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"533\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-24\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/55b7b318367adab4259993268ad4b31c8601e4bd-300x287.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"558\" height=\"534\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-25\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/8883e12a2834349bb6cae6e0c8ea15ce37d3be32-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"778\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-26\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/46562f4c510fd9f978dbdd0c242dd42a2934a432-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"543\" height=\"769\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-29\" src=\"http://merrier.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/fc93139759ee3d6dc1e20cae42166d224e4adeda-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"779\" />', 'PS常用颜色及代码', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ps%e5%b8%b8%e7%94%a8%e9%a2%9c%e8%89%b2%e5%8f%8a%e4%bb%a3%e7%a0%81', '', '', '2017-03-15 09:59:49', '2017-03-15 01:59:49', '', 0, 'http://merrier.com/?p=21', 0, 'post', '', 0),
